---
/**
 * Trust.astro
 * Section highlighting energy efficiency of local inference
 */
---

<section class="py-24 bg-rice-paper relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
         <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
             <!-- Content -->
             <div class="space-y-8">
                 <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal-ink">
                     Sustainable AI<br />
                     <span class="text-olive-growth italic font-medium">Energy That Stays Home</span>
                 </h2>

                 <div class="prose prose-lg text-charcoal-ink/90 font-body">
                     <p>
                        Cloud AI isn't just a privacy problemâ€”it's an energy problem. Every query travels through data centers burning electricity around the clock.
                     </p>
                     <p>
                        Local processing on your own hardware changes the equation. No servers. No transmission overhead. Just your chip doing what it was designed to do.
                     </p>
                 </div>

                 <ul class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm border-t-2 border-charcoal-ink/10 pt-8">
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                         <span>No data center overhead</span>
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                         <span>Zero network transmission energy</span>
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                         <span>Optimized for Apple Silicon efficiency</span>
                     </li>
                 </ul>
             </div>

             <!-- Visual: Big percentage callout -->
             <div class="relative">
                 <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-olive-growth/10 rounded-full blur-3xl z-0"></div>
                 <div class="relative z-10 bg-white border-2 border-charcoal-ink shadow-base p-10 text-center">
                     <span class="font-heading font-black text-7xl md:text-8xl text-olive-growth">&gt;75%</span>
                     <p class="font-heading text-2xl text-charcoal-ink mt-4">Less Energy</p>
                     <p class="font-mono text-sm text-charcoal-ink/60 mt-2">per query vs. cloud inference</p>
                 </div>
             </div>
         </div>
    </div>
</section>
